<inglise> - description of the work to be carried out, in particular the number of hectares concerned, the nature of the work and the geographical extent of the work; (1) OJ No C 269, 24.10.1979, p. 5. (2) Opinion delivered on 26 October 1979 (not yet published in the Official Journal). (3) OJ No L 94, 28.4.1970, p. 13. (4) OJ No L 117, 12.5.1979, p. 4. </inglise>
<eesti> - &uuml;ldise olukorra l&uuml;hike kirjeldus, eelk&otilde;ige seoses p&otilde;llumajandusele tekitatud kahjuga; - kavandatava t&ouml;&ouml; kirjeldus, eelk&otilde;ige asjaomaste hektarite arv, t&ouml;&ouml; laad ning t&ouml;&ouml; geograafiline ulatus; </eesti>
